{"id": 1102, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都无法忍受哪些早高峰礼仪破坏者？", "description": "大家都很急迫，互相留条活路好不好！（题图来自：Rod Hunt）", "record_count": 6350, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607102250343Zoa091zOTUDLIit.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-21T03:00:40Z", "options": [{"id": 100353, "content": "早高峰是什么？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591481}, {"id": 100358, "content": "开车忙手机，还占着车道爬行！有电话靠边啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345609}, {"id": 100359, "content": "走着走着突然停止，后面躲闪不及跟ta有点刮蹭就比比", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684658}, {"id": 100360, "content": "在公交车地铁吃韭菜馅的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673726}, {"id": 100361, "content": "一上电梯就好似僵尸一般木木的站着，留条通道让人走", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676491}, {"id": 100617, "content": "在封闭的车厢里吃着味道很浓郁的早餐，比如酸菜包…那酸爽…", "image": "img/option/option/20160722234330XJpUcdBEboD039Ya.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688252}, {"id": 101385, "content": "浑身汗臭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684832}, {"id": 100362, "content": "吃早餐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565016}, {"id": 100363, "content": "带小孩，小孩在车上大声嚷嚷家长跟没听见一样?", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 81259}, {"id": 100364, "content": "不排队", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685918}, {"id": 101906, "content": "写点什么呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692277}, {"id": 100372, "content": "公交卡，在刷卡时，被一个胖子生生撞！折！断！了.", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 243351}, {"id": 118549, "content": "走路低头玩手机，耳朵里塞着耳机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769047}, {"id": 100374, "content": "走路特慢我走这边他又走这边(｡-_-｡)", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685215}, {"id": 101654, "content": "大声打电话的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690875}, {"id": 100380, "content": "扶梯站在左边", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672227}, {"id": 100636, "content": "拿著煙街頭走到街尾。。\n還有兩三人并排慢行擋著路，討厭死", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688332}, {"id": 100381, "content": "上车一直有人在后面推你", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687107}, {"id": 100383, "content": "争路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687131}, {"id": 100384, "content": "乱插队，不顾他人想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685427}, {"id": 100385, "content": "玩手机走路慢！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525236}, {"id": 100386, "content": "一群溜达的老阿姨爷叔们", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671273}, {"id": 106788, "content": "时不时来上一句：“你**有病啊！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711860}, {"id": 100390, "content": "电动车乱闯线，这是急着干啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679453}, {"id": 100392, "content": "大爷大妈们就别在高峰点儿出行好不啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669692}, {"id": 100394, "content": "臭男人?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621654}, {"id": 100395, "content": "坐车前不准备好公交卡或者零钱，站在上车门口恨不得把包底都翻个洞！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223881}, {"id": 100396, "content": "上车的时候比谁都能挤，动作特利索，等车一发动就站不稳，年纪这么大就别挤早高峰了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584951}, {"id": 113453, "content": "几个人并排上楼或者堵着电梯的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747023}, {"id": 100398, "content": "1⃣️地铁堵门儿的\n2⃣️没下完使劲儿挤上车的\n3⃣️走路慢还横道儿中间走的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473239}, {"id": 100399, "content": "随便发屁?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687221}, {"id": 188975, "content": "在公共交通上吃味道好大的早餐！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980545}, {"id": 100402, "content": "最讨厌的就是人挤人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681110}, {"id": 100403, "content": "早上辦公室的電梯被自私的人霸佔己用，並一直停頓在某樓層。\n\n在密集的行人路上穿插的電動自行車和三輪車。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 374921}, {"id": 100918, "content": "坐公交车不让里面走。你自己懒得动也就算了，至少把路让开让别人进去啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171675}, {"id": 146999, "content": "早自习在教室吃早餐，特别是油条！！！各种馅儿的包子！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872723}, {"id": 100407, "content": "挡路的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678651}, {"id": 100408, "content": "上公交时 后面的大妈会用肘部顶你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433479}, {"id": 100410, "content": "这是怎么了", "image": "img/option/option/20160722015532aBE1xzGfu0ViN2F3.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687277}, {"id": 100426, "content": "看手机，走路慢，还挡道。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687306}, {"id": 100427, "content": "地铁里吃东西真心受不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197942}, {"id": 100429, "content": "在地铁吃东西还吧唧嘴的，真是无语。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679733}, {"id": 100174, "content": "走路慢，还一直挡着路", "image": null, "praise_count": 892, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391490}, {"id": 100430, "content": "???要下地铁的人都还没下完，上地铁的“浪”就涌进来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594873}, {"id": 100431, "content": "走路时候的低头族……自己的安全和别人的安全都有风险！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493367}, {"id": 100943, "content": "小学生公交还没靠站就跟丧尸一样围堵车门辣条味一车推搡打架", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689348}, {"id": 100176, "content": "抢我公交座位！", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686340}, {"id": 100432, "content": "在地铁or公交里吃着巨香的牛肉小笼包", "image": "img/option/option/20160722074644hImd6Upng0zt9YXE.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644807}, {"id": 100177, "content": "提前订好车，司机还是不准时，各种找不到路。", "image": null, "praise_count": 86, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431550}, {"id": 100433, "content": "扶手梯上真不会让出左边通道吗？！没发觉一楼梯精神攻击叠加打在你背后吗？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333212}]}